The evidence with the title 'Meles Zenawi - Wikipedia ' says Meles was elected member of the leadership committee in 1979 and chairman of the executive committee of TPLF in 1983 . He was the chairperson of both the TPLF and the EPRDF after the EPRDF assumed power at the end of the Ethiopian Civil War in 1991 . He was president of the transitional government of Ethiopia  ... 
